<br>
As for how much it costs...  like any real-life wedding, you spend what you can afford and make a budget. Some players I have seen have gotten matching dyed-plate suits, others spend on robes and such. But if you want guests, make sure you hire taxis to get people there, and you can have fireworks courtesy of your favorite casters... <br>
<br>
Side effects to a wedding or marriage? Well, I've know players who've gotten divorced... that's a possible side effect of marriage, period.<br>
<br>
